<br>
   For the barnacle breastplate, you have to kill a diseased shark, and then kill it's babies.  The diseased shark is around level 11, and the babies are around level 1.  Even a full group of level 4 players (assuming you could form such a group in Erudin) couldn't handle that (add to this the fact that there's a hammerhead shark around level 15 who shares the pool with the diseased one). <br>
<br>
   Can you do the quest?  Yes, but it generally requires hanging in the area as a newbie, begging higher level players to kill the diseased shark, or vice versa, which, when all is said and done, is really stupid.<br>
